  <brief_title>Home Monitoring for Atrial Fibrillation Using a Microlife Blood Pressure Monitor</brief_title>
  <acronym>TRIPPS</acronym>
  <official_title>Home Monitoring for Atrial Fibrillation Using a Microlife Blood Pressure Monitor: Trial of Regular vs Irregualr Pulse for the Prevention of Stroke (TRIPPS 2.0)</official_title>
